	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What are you trying to refer to when you say &quot;Cinemascope&quot;? The ancient capturing/projection method to get anamorphic widescreen content on a little square piece of film? Or are you just referring to &quot;ultra-wide&quot; TVs, or curved ones? Or 2:39:1 aspect ratio?<br /><br />Full-screen VHS movies were almost always pan-and-scan croppings of the original print. It's nice to fill a screen, but I don't miss that practice at the expense of parts of the original shot.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


